<plot>Tony has been in love with Mary for quite sometime, and they decide to be very intimate, and as a result Mary gets pregnant. Shortly after this, the police come looking for Tony, to charge him with murder, and Tony disappears. Mary gives birth to a daughter, Lily, and lives with Dr. Shambhunath and his wife. Years later, Tarun Kumar enters Mary's life and identifies himself as Tony. Mary is delighted and relieved. Unfortunately for Tony, Police Inspector Lawrence also recognizes him, and it is then Tony must decide to run away again or face arrest and imprisonment.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?143410</url></doc>
